Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for some advice in dealing with the lunatic fringe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I moderate the David R. Hawkins fan group,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's quite a lunatic fringe out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.49,0:01:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me question what good, if any, the group serves sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.93,0:01:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're just out there in force right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.49,0:01:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,which I'm sure you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes I get the same emails.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I mean, how do you deal with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it's like, do I help them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to do it with intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.50,0:01:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the intention behind the comment?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.56,0:01:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the intention of the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.56,0:01:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the intentionality of the positionality?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is served by that, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What we're presenting is the consequence of 50 years of psychiatry,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.52,0:01:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,psychoanalysis, psychology, psychotherapy, individual and group.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.89,0:01:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.57,0:01:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as my own personal psychoanalysis,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as transformative spiritual experiences,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as 25 years in consciousness research.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a really formidable body of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And somebody will pick out some trivial things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.28,0:02:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what's frustrating about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And the problem is not being able to tell the forest from the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And it isn't the trees, it's the forest that impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the impact of the work all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So some of them are quite against the grain to where sometimes they feel
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,like maybe I should just kick them out of the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they have the same, but most, what I've been doing is I just ignore them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they leave on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Or they get abusive, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When they get abusive, you say, what's the point of being abusive, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's not a psychotherapy group.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, you've got all kinds of un-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a psycho group.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a psycho group.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I sometimes advise psychotherapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly, your question really requires psychotherapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really an answer having anything to do with the work, you see what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, like this guy, what does he think he's going to get to God, whether it depends
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,on whales or dolphins?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know, it's got nothing to do with the thrust of the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it got to do with realizing the presence of God within as the self of the capitalist,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what you're dealing with is the ego, and the ego is impersonal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't forget, this work is the direct antithesis of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what you're getting-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.90,0:03:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The work threatens the narcissistic core of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the basis of all what you're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Within itself, the ego considers itself sovereign.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So, any kind of spiritual work is going to trigger hatred from the narcissistic ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,who says it is God.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the secular hates divinity, because it contradicts the ego's positionality that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it is the source of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The malignant narcissistic mania, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,As you see it, like, what's his name coming up for trial now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you see, there you're going to see the narcissistic ego laid bare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're dealing with is minor expressions, but it's coming from the same motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, any time we get a negative email, we'll ask what political position this person has.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They all come from the same political position.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:05:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what you've said antagonizes their view that narcissism should be the law of the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when dealing with that-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, is it more of a go on a case-by-case basis, what I feel the intention might be,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,or is it just be more strict on the guidelines?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we have this-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My purpose is I want the groups to serve the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have the same discussion sometimes, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How is, what's the best way to answer this, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And see that the person, you know, is the victim of their own ignorance, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, they will make negative comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And they haven't even read the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The percentage of people who have been vociferously antagonistic to the book,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,more than 2% have read the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,None of them have read the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They open to Chapter 9, they look up what their favorite positionality is,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,find you don't agree with it, then they write you a nasty letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't even read the book yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can tell by their commentary that they have no familiarity with the whole subject
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,about which they're commenting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, here's another minor question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Being that the name of the group is the Fan Group, and fan is short for fanatic,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is that a good name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should change it to the Hawkins Enthusiast Group or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think just discussion, you know, is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that works too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the work should be discussed, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because in the discussion, you see the air compelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the intentionality behind it is what reveals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So what sounds like an ignorance can actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a legitimate request for information.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some of that, but it's very...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's really some serious people out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, well, that works for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:07:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean, because we get some funny ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.47,0:07:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And some of them are so far out, we have what we call a Noodleheimer file.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I could probably add some names to that list for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We do have, and that's actually what it's called.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called the Noodleheimer file.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And those are from, you know, far out in left field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know if they're on the ballpark, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I was counting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we see 50% of the people are below 200, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the way I tried to screen them out in the first place
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,was I put in the beginning and the end of all my books,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloria in excelsis Deo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, that doesn't fry out an atheist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, he's got what's coming to him if he turns the next page.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't have said it better myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You could remind people of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the first salutation in the books?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Straight and narrow is the path, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And Gloria in excelsis Deo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why did you read any further?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first German book.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, don't know what you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too hard to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the German.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It says,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Das alle Sehende Auge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the all-seeing eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Das all Sehende.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's C.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,S-E-H-E is C.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And Auge is A-U-G-E is I.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the all-seeing eye when translated into German
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of the eye of the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Kallenbach arranged that translation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Supervised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:08:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank both you and Susan so much for all your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question from a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's a religious science minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.76,0:09:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack Blackman from Albuquerque, New Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Religious science, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And he asked me to ask this question for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He says that every day he prays
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to surrender his body,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,his mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,his spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,his will,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,his ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,his everything to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And he says that after a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,he started wondering,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,since everything is God,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,what is he surrendering?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's surrendering his illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was his question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you know, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,he's surrendering his personal self.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, inasmuch as there is no such thing as a personal self,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see what his paradox is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But so long as he thinks that it's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, God really doesn't need verbalization.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,God gets intention without verbalization.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's putting it in a linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I advise to live one's life as a mudra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, when you get up in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you picture yourself this way, the divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and divinity just got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He could try it non-verbally as a way of being instead of verbally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of using prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In which you yourself become a supplication,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,without verbalizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:10:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for answering his question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-verbal. Supplication.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say the kitty comes up to me and goes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,what can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to be a big kitty and just purr up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go to the storm and golly room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll appreciate everything you've said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-verbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-verbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I like religious answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We've spoken a lot at our churches, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You kind of answered my question, sort of, with hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:12:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was, how do we go about praying for each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And where do we go about praying for each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do we stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you pray for each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we, how, in, in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How would you pray for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,For their highest and best good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is in their highest and best good?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, when you pray for your children, for instance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I tend to non-verbalize it, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And more to hold it, to hold it forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And that which you hold in mind tends to materialize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It tends to come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a manifestation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if I picture the person as well, because, you know, a lot of times people are brought
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,around for healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I merely picture them as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the rest is a karmic propensity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not up to that which I, you know, to the personal self.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it isn't like an I wants to make a them better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a dualistic positionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That which I am sees them in their fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it doesn't, because it's also a karmic propensity, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, where do you stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, not, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Having done it once, it's sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you can remind God once in a while, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And Nellie's arthritis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't forgotten it, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I'd like to say thank you, and I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm grateful for all of your teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I love teaching, and the sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:14:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I'm on task, from the Maui Group, to invite you once again to Maui to visit us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Wayne Dyer would love to have you stay with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Maui?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Maui.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Maui!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were playing you were a kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Maui.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, recently I was reading Ramesh Bhalsakar in Consciousness Speaks, and he
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,stated that there is no individualized soul, and that the concept of a soul accumulating
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,negative or positive karma was bullshit, those were his words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And upon reading that, I put all my books away, I could no longer read anymore, and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of went through a bit of a hell for a few days, and that's real different than
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,what you teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:14:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So could you clarify that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I've kind of come to a recontextualization on my own, but could you clarify what he means
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That there's no individualized soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a subtle question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We notice that at the moment of birth, people calibrate differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that come about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my understanding through my recontextualization is that consciousness is expressing through
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that what he calls, Bhalsakar calls, the body-mind organism.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You just said there's no karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the body-mind organism, where'd that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't pre-exist, this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:16:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The body-mind organism comes out of creation, comes out of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he states.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, it's an accidental universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not accidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Random.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of random.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not random.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There is divine harmony and concordance, therefore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the Buddhic idea of karma being a circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You could be reborn a rabbit or a chicken or something, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore, there would be no karmic responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no karmic responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point to the teachings of Jesus Christ or the Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't agree with what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I tell you my recontextualization?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:17:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it was really devastating for me to read that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of went through this thing of almost becoming an atheist again, because it seemed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,like that kind of put it back to you're just being used by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nihilistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a nihilistic notion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I recontextualize it in that, the field of consciousness expresses through us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And so because that there is all of us, all of that that can be expressed through us,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,which is like that's why we have all of the different things on the scale, on the map
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness that we can experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like the collective consciousness of man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And so through karmic merit, like in the next life or this life, you experience a more
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,positive life through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmic merit is individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:18:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So I shouldn't read Bhalsakar anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It contradicts every spiritual teaching I'm aware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, because I focused on your works very seriously for the last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It contradicts every spiritual teaching I've ever experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read or studied or discovered through research.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well it didn't make sense to me either, and that's why I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't the Buddha teach what he taught, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To avoid reincarnation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So who is it that's avoiding reincarnation then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The individual soul, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But if everything is God and everything is consciousness and we all go back to oneness...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a random intellectualization, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's confusing the real with the hypothetical.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's hypothetical.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the real.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when you're born, you're born with a calibrated level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And you weren't born in Las Vegas on a green table.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll take the words of Jesus Christ and the Buddha over Ramesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent some days with him, and at that time he was in a pretty good state.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it served me in that it helped break through a lot of ego and victimhood stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that I worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come to my meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We go through all those phases.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.64,0:19:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really nihilistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.98,0:19:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if he's still living or...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:20:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I want to sincerely thank you for sharing with us and being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's certainly changed my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.48,0:20:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The question I have is, you speak of natural, spontaneous, spiritual phenomenon happening
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,as you're on that path to enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you speak of it, I have a very deep, profound understanding of it, although I can
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,honestly say I don't think I've ever experienced that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is, can you intuitively share that experience with a wise, mystic teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Avatar, without actually going through it yourself to still be on that path?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Share what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, for instance, like you even talk about kundalini energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I know what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it necessary to experience that, to be on the path?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Or can one intuitively share that experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The kundalini energy automatically begins to flow at consciousness level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of it creates the etheric body, the etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Prior to consciousness level 200, people have a group karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I didn't finish answering what she said, but below 200, what we get is you have group
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, below 200, if you calibrate at 140, you share the karmic consequences of that group.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.78,0:21:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Animals have a group karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only over 200 that you have an individual karmic destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What I said was the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the sheep inherit sheepness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And they are all sheepnesses together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But over 200, now you're personally accountable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.75,0:21:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're personally accountable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything has a karmic consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now you have individual responsibility, not just group.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.96,0:22:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the human has both individual and group karmic propensities.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That which has been earned, that which is still due.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.67,0:22:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're saying that,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.67,0:22:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, you have the ability to progress, for lack of a better word, and I know that's
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.83,0:22:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,not probably the correct word, but you will naturally have those phenomenon?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The emergence is at level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't really experience it as the so-called cities until maybe 550.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.60,0:22:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.60,0:22:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They start flowing around 550.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.60,0:22:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.60,0:22:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They start flowing over 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.81,0:22:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.81,0:22:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As you get into the 500s, you begin to feel this exquisite energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.29,0:22:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And will you always recognize that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.29,0:22:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.29,0:22:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.67,0:22:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.67,0:23:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It beats orgasms all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.67,0:23:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to debate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.14,0:23:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.14,0:23:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, it's continuous, continuous, continuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.14,0:23:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.23,0:23:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, did the level of karmic karmic propensities,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.23,0:23:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,did the level of consciousness of the world rise after the World Day of Prayer this last
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.23,0:23:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,September the 8th?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It rose the last time we were in San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.54,0:23:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What, November 2003?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.54,0:23:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.54,0:23:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, 2003.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.54,0:23:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There was the Harmonic Concordance at that time, World Day of Prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.54,0:23:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And it went up two points, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.54,0:23:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know, 515, it was 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.60,0:23:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And at 530, it was 207.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.60,0:24:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.67,0:24:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the Unity Day of Prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.84,0:24:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,On the 8th of September.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.96,0:24:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt the One Day of Prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.12,0:24:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness level of mankind, we have permission to ask that, is still at 207.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.12,0:24:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's at 208.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.12,0:24:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still at 207.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.12,0:24:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We just dropped something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.12,0:24:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.19,0:24:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.25,0:24:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.25,0:24:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, you can't look at it as cause and effect in a mathematical, like arithmetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.25,0:24:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.67,0:24:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow piles up, and then when the temperature and humidity and all is right, the avalanche occurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.63,0:24:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But today didn't cause the avalanche.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.72,0:24:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So the collective positive karma of mankind, you might say, when large groups pray, you're building it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.30,0:24:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it breaks forth at the propitious time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.30,0:25:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's immeasurable, you know, from day to day in sort of a mathematical kind of a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.59,0:25:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.53,0:25:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say you get like a collective merit, and eventually the momentum of it brings it across the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.79,0:25:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.79,0:25:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.79,0:25:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.42,0:25:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.19,0:25:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.56,0:25:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're taking pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.27,0:25:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, pictures, pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.27,0:25:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how to work those machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.75,0:25:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind I get in Walgreens, my cameras, I get them in Walgreens, use them up, and throw them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.75,0:25:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks good, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.64,0:26:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.99,0:26:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.99,0:26:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.31,0:26:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for your teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.31,0:26:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I was last here in April, and started to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.49,0:26:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.80,0:26:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Can one person steal or draw energy from another person?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.76,0:26:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,People below 200 drain energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.76,0:26:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,People above 200 give energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.76,0:26:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you spend time with people below 200, they would drain your energy if you're above 200?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.24,0:26:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, unless you have some particular – see, when I was a psychiatrist and I was dealing with it, practically everybody was below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.04,0:27:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was protected by – let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.18,0:27:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was protected by the role – oh, I was protected by the energy field of the role, R-O-L-E.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.24,0:27:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was protected by the energy field of the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.24,0:27:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if instead of treating them in the office, I was partying with them someplace, I probably would have had my energy drained by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.53,0:27:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's wise to stay away from people with low energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.53,0:27:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.75,0:27:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how to ask that correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.75,0:27:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on the field you're interfering with.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.39,0:27:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's –
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.39,0:27:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.39,0:27:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.39,0:27:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In general, you see, the basic teaching is to stay with holy people.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.39,0:27:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang out with holy people.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.58,0:27:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And avoid those which are negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.58,0:27:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And that teaching is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.14,0:27:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We get fleas that lie down with dogs, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.14,0:28:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So the basic teaching is to hang out with holy people.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.52,0:28:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And to say goodbye to those that are less than 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.52,0:28:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You do what you can for them, and then you send them out of your way, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.21,0:28:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.42,0:28:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because the energy drain gets to be endless.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.42,0:28:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,First they borrow the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.77,0:28:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they don't pay the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.77,0:28:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they borrow your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.77,0:28:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they –
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.77,0:28:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they've got your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.77,0:28:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't fix your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.48,0:28:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I lent it to a guy one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.48,0:28:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.48,0:28:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.48,0:28:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you feel sorry for somebody, you're being hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.54,0:28:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So I felt sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.54,0:28:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So I lent him my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.54,0:28:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Two months later, I had to get somebody else to drive me over to his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.64,0:28:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The car was in his driveway with the keys in it, the windows open, the rain and all coming in all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.80,0:28:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had to retrieve my own car.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.89,0:28:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.89,0:28:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets worse and worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.89,0:28:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The next thing I know, he reneged on a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.89,0:29:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The next thing I know, he'd left the country, escaped to Canada.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.88,0:29:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably had so much behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.14,0:29:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's its own answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.04,0:29:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't get better, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.88,0:29:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Jesus said not to oppose them but to avoid them is what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.95,0:29:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.40,0:29:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.40,0:29:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.40,0:29:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What advice would you give to someone approaching the recovery of an ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.56,0:29:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.56,0:29:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is approaching the recovery of an eating disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.56,0:29:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.20,0:29:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What advice would you give?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.52,0:29:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the eating disorders, you know, are a complicated treatment program.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.52,0:29:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I was a psychiatrist at a place called Pia's Place, we treated lots of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.52,0:29:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a complicated problem and a complicated treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.52,0:29:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was never really enthusiastic about it, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.74,0:29:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So do you have, like, a method you would recommend or you just don't know how to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.74,0:29:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.74,0:29:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.74,0:29:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.74,0:29:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.74,0:29:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.44,0:29:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.44,0:29:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.44,0:29:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.44,0:29:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.44,0:29:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.54,0:29:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.54,0:29:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.54,0:29:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.54,0:29:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.54,0:29:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.54,0:29:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.54,0:29:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.54,0:30:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.24,0:30:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.24,0:30:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.24,0:30:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.24,0:30:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.43,0:30:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was never really enthusiastic about it, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.43,0:30:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So do you have, like, a method you would recommend or you just don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.43,0:30:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's usually a composite of individual therapy, sometimes psychopharmacology and group therapy
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.43,0:30:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,all at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.43,0:30:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.52,0:30:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.58,0:30:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, as you just prepped a storm, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.58,0:30:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It was always difficult and complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.06,0:30:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a simple one to one kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.06,0:30:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I come bearing the gift of my two favorite beverages.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.26,0:30:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I discovered that-
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.76,0:30:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I may share.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.88,0:30:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, espresso.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.04,0:30:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.60,0:30:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My favorite beverage is my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.40,0:30:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt so much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.24,0:30:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.44,0:30:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.48,0:30:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you for validating that part of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.92,0:30:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.18,0:30:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Late last summer, or this summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.84,0:31:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,as I was reading the book for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.12,0:31:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote you an email that went something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.32,0:31:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch, ouch, ouch, ouch, ouch, ouch, ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.34,0:31:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Band-Aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.60,0:31:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Like ripping off Band-Aids.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.70,0:31:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a cute one.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.52,0:31:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She was.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.98,0:31:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We put it up on the bulletin board.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.72,0:31:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the sound of me reading your book.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.58,0:31:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, I think, is I believe how the rest of it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.16,0:31:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a cute email.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.88,0:31:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning you mentioned about being enamored,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.66,0:31:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm still enamored with something,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.36,0:31:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm hoping you can help me with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.22,0:31:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's not specifically mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.76,0:31:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a big fan of the Book of Job.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.67,0:31:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Book of Job.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.73,0:31:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I like his story.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.47,0:31:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that in the Old Testament?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.55,0:31:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.25,0:31:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I like his story,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.27,0:31:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,because it has a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.79,0:31:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And because it mirrors my experience
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.55,0:31:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,of when I began to seek God,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.07,0:31:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,my life fell apart in oh so many ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.97,0:31:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And that continues to be my experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.55,0:31:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Though my reaction to it changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.89,0:31:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do I need to let go of that one, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.78,0:32:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My enamoredness of the book?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.06,0:32:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it isn't the book itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.26,0:32:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it about the book that you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.08,0:32:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.10,0:32:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it integrity?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.90,0:32:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how awful things got,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.98,0:32:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that in the end, how did Job make out?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.70,0:32:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he made out really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.80,0:32:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.26,0:32:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a happy ending?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.38,0:32:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.04,0:32:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All was restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.46,0:32:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I read that correctly?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.38,0:32:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.40,0:32:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then why worry about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.23,0:32:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, does it calibrate high enough to still be included?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.15,0:32:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you didn't mention it, and that made me...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.37,0:32:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.23,0:32:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It made me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.37,0:32:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That it was more fantasy than...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.29,0:32:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really a test of his faith, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.31,0:32:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.87,0:32:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happened, Job chose God.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.01,0:32:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's a very positive thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.74,0:32:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hang on to that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.84,0:32:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.78,0:32:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.64,0:32:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.38,0:32:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one of my favorites, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.88,0:32:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In the pits of hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.92,0:32:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,where there isn't even the thought of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.98,0:32:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.21,0:33:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandon hope, all ye who enter here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.79,0:33:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the gruesome truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.58,0:33:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to thank both you, Dr. Hawkins and Susan,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.48,0:33:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,for everything that you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.16,0:33:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.08,0:33:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't recall you addressing,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.64,0:33:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm taking this to a great length,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.62,0:33:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but the period of time between incarnations is...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.30,0:33:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,As individuals, do we wait until there's that...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.64,0:33:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the best time, best circumstances to be born into?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.02,0:33:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not an authority on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.57,0:33:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that when you leave the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.33,0:33:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,like goes to like.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.31,0:33:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You gravitate to a spiritual realm
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.40,0:33:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that is aligned with...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.98,0:33:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,with what you have become, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.98,0:33:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.48,0:34:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, from some of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.48,0:34:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,my intuitive understanding is
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.51,0:34:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it's optional, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.51,0:34:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's optional.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.98,0:34:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.48,0:34:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.98,0:34:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're still attached to things of this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.98,0:34:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you're gonna naturally choose yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.04,0:34:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, this world calls...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.04,0:34:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,affords optimal modes of karmic resolution,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.54,0:34:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,restitution for a negative karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.54,0:34:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.07,0:34:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So some people might choose it,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.07,0:34:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,because this is my opportunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.07,0:34:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to undo that which I wish I had not done at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.57,0:34:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.57,0:34:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.07,0:34:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So because of the karmic opportunity here...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.07,0:34:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.93,0:34:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So to get over the guilt of undoing what I had done to others,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.02,0:34:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.02,0:34:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.52,0:34:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I know at a certain level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.02,0:34:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,where I would get these terrible pains all over,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.78,0:34:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I would calibrate the one in me
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.84,0:35:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,who was violently abusive to others,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.07,0:35:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and I would get yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.07,0:35:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.73,0:35:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I experienced violent abuse myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.24,0:35:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought, where did I come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.24,0:35:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been violently abusive to anybody in this lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.24,0:35:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.24,0:35:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.24,0:35:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So it could be in this lifetime we get to undo.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.82,0:35:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Undo.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.82,0:35:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So we may choose the karmic option to undo
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.82,0:35:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,for the sake of our own spiritual salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.32,0:35:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.44,0:35:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we own up to some of those things,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.94,0:35:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as you said, you begin to experience those feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.44,0:35:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that you'd never acted on any of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.44,0:35:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So just the realization that you had done those things
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.44,0:35:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in another lifetime...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.94,0:35:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I think if you see it within your own consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.44,0:35:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you can undo it with strictly spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.61,0:35:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it with strictly spiritual techniques, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.43,0:35:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,See, there's two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.43,0:36:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's responsibility and there's answerability.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.56,0:36:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the correct word.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.06,0:36:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.59,0:36:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's the degree of guilt in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.91,0:36:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they call that word?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.91,0:36:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Culpability.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.91,0:36:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Culpability, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.91,0:36:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think we can undo one by spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.04,0:36:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think the other one you may have to undo.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.39,0:36:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.39,0:36:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So it has to do with the balance between culpability and responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.39,0:36:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So I may innocently kill somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.39,0:36:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and not be really culpable.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.93,0:36:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm still responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.12,0:36:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.83,0:36:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.82,0:36:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So culpability is the degree of knowingness
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.82,0:36:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,with which a thing is done, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.82,0:36:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.82,0:36:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.82,0:36:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, you owe a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.59,0:36:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so even if accidentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.59,0:36:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, even, you know, you still didn't pay off the note,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.59,0:36:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,even though you went...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.59,0:36:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't mean to go bankrupt,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.59,0:37:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but you still owe the money, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.59,0:37:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.59,0:37:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's a degree of guilt in courts, say.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.59,0:37:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the circumstances, the degree of culpability.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.16,0:37:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think choosing reincarnation has to do with that balance
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.16,0:37:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,between culpability and responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.29,0:37:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So you may not be able to undo a certain thing just with good wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.29,0:37:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have to actually do it, be of service to others, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.29,0:37:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not an authority on the inner planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.15,0:37:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.73,0:37:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.05,0:37:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question about allness and nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.08,0:37:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.08,0:37:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a young boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.08,0:37:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.08,0:37:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You realized what?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.08,0:37:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.08,0:37:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.08,0:38:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I used to wake up at night in a cold sweat,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.08,0:38:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,realizing that maybe I wouldn't be,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.08,0:38:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and the thought of nothingness...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.08,0:38:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.08,0:38:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...scared the poop out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.08,0:38:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.08,0:38:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your teaching has helped me greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.08,0:38:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All fear is an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.43,0:38:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a conservation of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.43,0:38:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the back of your new book,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.43,0:38:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you say now even at a higher level,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.43,0:38:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,there was again that fluctuation between allness and nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.43,0:38:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you help me with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.43,0:38:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.43,0:38:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Allness versus nothingness comes up at about 850.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.94,0:38:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the ultimate reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.87,0:38:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the error of the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.21,0:38:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The error of the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.44,0:38:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The pathway of negation is to negate the reality of all that is linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.69,0:38:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.48,0:38:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wang Po, the aphorisms of Wang Po,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.92,0:38:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,will take you to 850.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.36,0:39:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But then you're in the void, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.36,0:39:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.36,0:39:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The void is extremely impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.36,0:39:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Very, very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.40,0:39:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.40,0:39:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-linear, eternal, ultimate peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.52,0:39:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was lacking the energy of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.96,0:39:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,which is overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.96,0:39:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So, early in life, I'd experienced the presence as infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.41,0:39:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of love which cannot be described beyond all description.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.92,0:39:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the void was sterile in comparison to the presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.50,0:39:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I backed out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.63,0:39:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.63,0:39:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There was exactly one thought left in the space,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.63,0:39:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and it took me hours to give that thought energy
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.63,0:39:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and pull myself back out of nothingness, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.63,0:39:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wang Po himself, interestingly,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.46,0:39:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,if you follow Wang Po, the pathway of negation,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.46,0:39:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll end up in the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.36,0:40:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wang Po himself later evolved to like 960.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.36,0:40:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wang Po stopped writing at that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.71,0:40:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But then he himself went on later and transcended 850.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.71,0:40:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And he himself got up to about 960 before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.71,0:40:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But he didn't write after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.71,0:40:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So everybody thinks that Wang Po,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.19,0:40:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,which we call as the Wang Po, is the ultimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.41,0:40:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's the ultimate to the void,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.41,0:40:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but the void is not the absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.41,0:40:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very interesting story
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.85,0:40:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that later after he stopped writing,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.85,0:40:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,he realized the mistake, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.85,0:40:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this will be in my aura,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.27,0:40:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,so whenever that occurs, I will know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.27,0:40:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing about the void is it's infinite,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.87,0:40:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,still, eternal, out of time, out of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.87,0:40:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no personal self, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.87,0:40:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The arhat, A-r-h-a-t, is an adept who reaches 800,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.56,0:41:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and to them that is the ultimate state.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.56,0:41:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not the ultimate state.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.46,0:41:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha himself calibrated a thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.28,0:41:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and he himself calibrated a thousand, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.28,0:41:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So did Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.48,0:41:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So 850 is not the ultimate state,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.48,0:41:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's extremely impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.02,0:41:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't fault anybody for not thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.02,0:41:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the enlightened state
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.02,0:41:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,because it is very, very, very, very profound
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.02,0:41:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and eternal, and eternal, and eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.44,0:41:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's only because of the prior experience
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.44,0:41:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that I realized there was something missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.77,0:41:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The mistake is in seeing love
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.90,0:41:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,as an attachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.06,0:41:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's a local teacher who was in a good space
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.06,0:41:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,until he began to teach that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.06,0:41:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is an attachment, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.25,0:41:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Personal love is an attachment between a me and a you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.25,0:41:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dualistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.25,0:41:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to have you, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.25,0:41:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You try and leave me, I'll kill you, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.25,0:42:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I'll kill myself, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.25,0:42:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.25,0:42:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a cleanliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.67,0:42:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So that kind of love, yes, you should release on, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.67,0:42:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But what's the lack of knowledge is that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.08,0:42:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the presence of divinity is the infinite presence of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.08,0:42:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you avoid love as a reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.08,0:42:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you've just avoided one of the major qualities of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.08,0:42:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So that teacher later went down
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.60,0:42:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,as a result of that mistaken teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.95,0:42:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.95,0:42:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.95,0:42:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.95,0:42:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.95,0:42:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Refuse anything as the ultimate, be grateful for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.95,0:42:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but demand that that which is love be present, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.17,0:42:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And the presence of God tells you it is the presence of love of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.17,0:42:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence of the infinite state is so radiant with love
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.17,0:42:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's unmistakable.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.17,0:42:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no question.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.17,0:42:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.17,0:42:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The void is very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.40,0:42:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not putting it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.40,0:42:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Very, very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.40,0:43:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Went into it in this lifetime back a couple times
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.72,0:43:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,going through the path of re-indigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.72,0:43:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It would recur.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.26,0:43:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I knew the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.84,0:43:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've taught us.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.84,0:43:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.96,0:43:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a very advanced question.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.97,0:43:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, sometimes there's present this very dark energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.84,0:43:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's what?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.84,0:43:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A dark energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.84,0:43:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.84,0:43:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And it feels like it's from without,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.84,0:43:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,just spitting out hatred towards me and life in general.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.09,0:43:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all the way without
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.16,0:43:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,or is it somewhat a projection from within to without?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.16,0:43:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.89,0:44:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You experience it in a space
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.89,0:44:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,or within your aura or?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.89,0:44:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like it's just out here attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.89,0:44:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an out there-ness.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.89,0:44:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.88,0:44:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And is it non-human?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.88,0:44:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, just dark, this dark blob.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.88,0:44:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark blob of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.88,0:44:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.23,0:44:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.23,0:44:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So you concretized it, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.23,0:44:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,given it a certain linearity, pictorial.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.23,0:44:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know if it's out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.03,0:44:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Refuse it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.53,0:44:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.53,0:44:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a karmic right to refuse it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.01,0:44:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She has the right to refuse it,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.40,0:44:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,rebuke it,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.43,0:44:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and demand that it leave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.00,0:44:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You can demand it and order.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.48,0:44:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There is in Christianity called,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.48,0:44:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it, the verification of spirits,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.89,0:44:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.89,0:44:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,People in the audience or somebody knows what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.89,0:45:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in which I ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.62,0:45:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,do you worship Jesus as Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.78,0:45:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can demand of a spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.78,0:45:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can demand that it speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.20,0:45:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is not of Jesus Christ or of the Lord or of God
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.20,0:45:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.20,0:45:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It cannot say yes that it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.20,0:45:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you demand that it leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.58,0:45:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And demand that in the name of Jesus Christ
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.58,0:45:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Lord God Almighty and the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.58,0:45:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that you leave me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.80,0:45:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And that it must leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.14,0:45:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the karmic power and right to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.14,0:45:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She has the karmic right to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.59,0:45:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you have the karmic right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.59,0:45:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.80,0:45:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Demand that it leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.80,0:45:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It will.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.63,0:45:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with discarnates.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.63,0:45:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll try and hang out with you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.63,0:45:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and you demand that they leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.63,0:45:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby demand in the name of Jesus Christ,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.84,0:45:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.84,0:46:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever you call divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.26,0:46:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that you leave me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.26,0:46:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And it must leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.11,0:46:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I know why it must leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.11,0:46:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because if it was of the highest order,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.11,0:46:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it wouldn't be hanging around around you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.86,0:46:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to torment people.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.86,0:46:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you demand that it leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.68,0:46:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called, what is it,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.08,0:46:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the clarification of spirits,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.08,0:46:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,or the...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.08,0:46:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Discernment.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.21,0:46:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The what?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.21,0:46:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Discernment.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.21,0:46:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Discernment of spirits, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.31,0:46:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The discernment of spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.31,0:46:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You just demand that it leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.47,0:46:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And it will leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.47,0:46:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.47,0:46:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't, you call me up,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.10,0:46:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come over and kick the hell out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.39,0:46:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get the bagpipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.22,0:46:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.22,0:46:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.22,0:46:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.22,0:46:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll call up the bagpipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.44,0:46:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just march.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.15,0:46:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn 180 and march, march away.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.15,0:46:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.11,0:47:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.11,0:47:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.11,0:47:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.11,0:47:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.13,0:47:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What did they say of spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.13,0:47:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Discernment.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.74,0:47:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Discernment.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.74,0:47:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I always forget the word discernment.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.74,0:47:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I always think it's clarification of spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.74,0:47:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Discernment.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.74,0:47:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.16,0:47:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question about kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.28,0:47:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had several healthcare people use it on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.35,0:47:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was always incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.35,0:47:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I just became crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.35,0:47:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.47,0:47:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.47,0:47:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.47,0:47:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.66,0:47:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.66,0:47:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was listening to your CD,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.66,0:47:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and in there you said I think 10% of people wasn't able to use kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.75,0:47:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's 10% of the population in general,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.75,0:48:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,for reasons unknown, karmic generally.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.23,0:48:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, about a third of the population is all that can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.23,0:48:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,People below 200 can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.23,0:48:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That gets you to 50%.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.32,0:48:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So is it them or is it me that they can't ... It doesn't seem to ever be correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.55,0:48:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I just get sicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.55,0:48:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, who's using the kinesiology?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.55,0:48:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You or the practitioner?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.55,0:48:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The practitioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.55,0:48:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And the practitioner's answer is that you were wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.44,0:48:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I get sicker rather than it helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.44,0:48:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know other people who have gone to these people and seemingly have gotten help,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.73,0:48:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's never worked for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.15,0:48:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it may not be the right pathway for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.61,0:48:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.61,0:48:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.61,0:48:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's many reasons why a person gets sicker well,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.61,0:48:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,having nothing to do with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.84,0:49:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they're usually advising me to take certain vitamins or certain supplements.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.84,0:49:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.84,0:49:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.19,0:49:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.19,0:49:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, people put over expectations on nutrition a lot of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.19,0:49:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They are helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.19,0:49:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't cure a brain tumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.11,0:49:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.11,0:49:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They're helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.11,0:49:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.49,0:49:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It sets up the environment to be favorable for healing, but it may not be sufficient
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.49,0:49:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,in and of itself, depending on what the diagnosis is.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.49,0:49:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.15,0:49:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm still kind of confused as that's not the road for me to go or ...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.15,0:49:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're just talking about holistic health.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.15,0:49:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not talking about a doctor prescribing a medication, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.15,0:49:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they're practitioners.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.15,0:49:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.15,0:49:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not an MD who's prescribing a drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.15,0:49:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a chiropractor or ...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.15,0:49:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.15,0:49:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So why don't you try a regular MD?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.15,0:49:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they don't use kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.15,0:49:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, if you've got something wrong with you, any doctor can diagnose it and treat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.47,0:49:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not exactly out of this world in this mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.47,0:49:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.47,0:49:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, can you do it to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.47,0:49:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a way of testing yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.76,0:49:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just worry about getting well and forget about all these diagnostic techniques?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.76,0:49:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it probably sounds like what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.76,0:49:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it probably sounds like what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.76,0:50:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it probably sounds like what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.76,0:50:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it probably sounds like what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.76,0:50:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it probably sounds like what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.76,0:50:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it probably sounds like what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.76,0:50:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I've finally come to that conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.76,0:50:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've got migraine, you take Imatrix.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.76,0:50:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It cures it in 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.76,0:50:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.76,0:50:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to go to a practitioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.76,0:50:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do the kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.76,0:50:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to take the nutritionist.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.76,0:50:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can cure it in 20 minutes flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.76,0:50:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Try that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.76,0:50:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.08,0:50:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.08,0:50:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.08,0:50:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a way of testing yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.08,0:50:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just worry about getting well and forget about all these diagnostic techniques?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.08,0:50:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it probably sounds like what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.08,0:50:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I've finally come to, that conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.08,0:50:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've got migraine, you take Imatrix.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.08,0:50:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It cures it in 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.08,0:50:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.08,0:50:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying? I don't have to go to a practitioner, I don't have to do a physiology, I don't have to take a nutritionist, I can cure it in 20 minutes flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.34,0:50:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Try that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.34,0:50:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have the headache cured before they've even finished with all this crap, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.27,0:50:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, these are long-standing health issues that I've had.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.27,0:50:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know, you're being too vague about it, that's too much of a generality, I can't answer you on a generality.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.27,0:50:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of health issue? There's no such diagnosis, specifically what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.27,0:51:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I had irritable bowel.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.27,0:51:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you on any kind of medication for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.55,0:51:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,At this time, it's doing okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.38,0:51:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,At this time, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.38,0:51:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's doing alright at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.38,0:51:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of have to figure out for myself what's the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.38,0:51:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so your intention, eventually you're going to win with it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.38,0:51:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.38,0:51:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's spasmodic, you watch the things that aggravate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.38,0:51:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have lots of allergies.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.89,0:51:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the trouble with alternate medicine is a lot of times it gets into a make-wrong of traditional medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.89,0:51:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,With traditional medicine, I usually had a person cured before they could make the appointment with the alternate medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.89,0:51:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.89,0:51:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if traditional medicine doesn't work, you try alternate.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.89,0:51:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're phobic about medical doctors and scared of them, and a lot of people are.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.24,0:51:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.24,0:51:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you try the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.24,0:51:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But by the time nutrition gets around to healing something, you're going to be considerably older than you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.24,0:52:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not old enough, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.34,0:52:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All those things are supportive, but they're not curative.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.79,0:52:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.79,0:52:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And a lot of times, all you need is the support and the situation will resolve itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.79,0:52:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But then sometimes you need a specific on top of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.81,0:52:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to treat complicated mental disorders.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.48,0:52:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And all the holistic things we did were added to the traditional.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.80,0:52:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was very hard not to recover if you followed what we did there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.19,0:52:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Or a person would be on a traditional treatment, and as soon as we added the nutritional, they promptly got better.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.64,0:52:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So you try to treat the overall person, and at the same time the specifics as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.96,0:52:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I would go both traditional and non-traditional simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.59,0:53:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A good holistic practitioner isn't going to feel offended if you're also seeing a regular doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.35,0:53:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not if he's integrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.41,0:53:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, my patients, anything they can do to make them better, I'm all for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.51,0:53:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I just thought, I just was curious if I was one of those that it just isn't readable.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.64,0:53:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it, I doubt it, I doubt it, I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.64,0:53:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt that you're, you know, incurable.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.64,0:53:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.64,0:53:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.64,0:53:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're better already.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.64,0:53:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're better than you were five minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.64,0:53:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you some gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.59,0:53:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My group in Youngstown, Ohio sent those to you and Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.59,0:53:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you enjoy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.59,0:53:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the same one I have on.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.59,0:53:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have a study group of your book, Eye of the Eye, which is really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.59,0:53:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.59,0:54:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're studying the Quartz and Miracles at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.59,0:54:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.59,0:54:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And the question that I have, I was fascinated by your horse story.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.59,0:54:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,By my what?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.59,0:54:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The horse story.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.59,0:54:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The horse story.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.78,0:54:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you didn't get along with horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.78,0:54:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.78,0:54:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And they didn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.78,0:54:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounded to me like you changed your karma today when you forgave the horses so that
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.78,0:54:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you could get along with the horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.78,0:54:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I love that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.78,0:54:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.78,0:54:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the same way or the same technique that I can use to change karma that I have
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.78,0:54:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.78,0:54:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgive everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.26,0:54:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.32,0:54:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In my...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.32,0:54:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens to you, the safest presumption is that what you've done to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.06,0:54:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're going to have to heal your guilt about having done that to others and the undoingness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.09,0:55:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of that and that you refuse that way and you choose instead to be kindly and forgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.09,0:55:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.15,0:55:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get concrete about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.15,0:55:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm not quite sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.15,0:55:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, like I was killed in a car crash when I was 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.49,0:55:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.49,0:55:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She was killed in a car crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.49,0:55:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.49,0:55:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.49,0:55:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.49,0:55:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means probably in a much earlier previous life, I probably killed that particular person.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.32,0:55:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And so what I need to do is just forgive any of those types.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.32,0:55:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I'm lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.32,0:55:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.32,0:55:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.32,0:55:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She's alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.32,0:55:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you were killed in a car crash when you were 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.68,0:55:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.68,0:55:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.68,0:55:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.32,0:55:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.32,0:55:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.32,0:55:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.75,0:55:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.75,0:55:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.75,0:55:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.75,0:55:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a teenager.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.75,0:55:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.75,0:55:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.75,0:55:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just using that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.75,0:55:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So did you have an out-of-body experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.75,0:55:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.75,0:55:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.75,0:55:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She was killed in a car wreck and had an out-of-body experience so she figures that she was
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.75,0:55:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In this life time?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.75,0:55:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.75,0:56:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In this life time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.75,0:56:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So she figures that
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.75,0:56:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How were you killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.75,0:56:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,By a drunk driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.75,0:56:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Her part probably stopped and she had an out-of-body experience and then came back into her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.32,0:56:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you died and then revived again?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.32,0:56:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.32,0:56:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.51,0:56:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You have questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.51,0:56:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that undid that one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.99,0:56:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She felt that maybe she had done that to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.37,0:56:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I think very likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.05,0:56:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She says maybe she had done that to someone else, and that's what the karmic...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.95,0:56:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.06,0:56:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Always presume that whatever happens to you
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.38,0:56:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is either the consequence of something you're holding in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.59,0:56:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,or it's the undoing of some karmic thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.43,0:56:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So the presumption is,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.29,0:56:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason I didn't get along with horses
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.45,0:56:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is because I've been brutal to horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.41,0:56:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I asked for kinesiology,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.57,0:56:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,in previous lifetimes, was I brutal to horses?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.93,0:56:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, yes, you'd get drunk, and you'd be angry, and you'd beat the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.24,0:57:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder the horse killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.74,0:57:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder I couldn't get along with horses in this lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.83,0:57:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So I had to forgive the one of me who was brutal and cruel to animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.55,0:57:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,forgive the horses for protecting himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.80,0:57:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and since then, I've got a picture at home of kissing a horse,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.42,0:57:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,which I never could have done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.68,0:57:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.08,0:57:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.66,0:57:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,An attitude of forgiveness about everything, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.68,0:57:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.76,0:57:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the cars and miracles works, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.24,0:57:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.98,0:57:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.72,0:57:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But the presumption, the presumption,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.10,0:57:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that if everybody's rude to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.37,0:57:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to forgive the one in you who is rude to others,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.61,0:57:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and unfeeling towards hurting their feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.75,0:57:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,For all lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.21,0:57:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.41,0:57:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And that will...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.45,0:57:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That will undo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.47,0:57:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Undo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.05,0:57:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All you need is the willingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.07,0:57:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.47,0:57:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, you know, see, one of the things I don't want to do
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.89,0:57:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is to...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.69,0:57:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is to come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.43,0:57:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.75,0:57:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't resist it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.39,0:57:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.57,0:58:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You get what you resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.85,0:58:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.57,0:58:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, whether you return or not, I'll leave up to God's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.53,0:58:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.03,0:58:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I could probably make a better decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.97,0:58:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding, just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.37,0:58:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.17,0:58:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.17,0:58:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,David, it's already worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.00,0:58:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.18,0:58:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always doing this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.80,0:58:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.20,0:58:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the timekeeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.52,0:58:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.98,0:58:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.58,0:58:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.58,0:58:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster, faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.00,0:58:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because he asked me such interesting questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.36,0:58:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.12,0:58:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I have two questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.14,0:58:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,One's individual and one's global.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.12,0:58:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The first is, in my current level of being,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.40,0:58:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,there seems to be some experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.56,0:58:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know your level of being draws your life
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.46,0:58:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,from what you're saying in the material
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.22,0:58:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and others are saying as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.54,0:58:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it seems as though,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.88,0:58:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and I haven't tested my level of beingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.68,0:58:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that you experience sometimes different levels,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.58,0:59:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,even though your level is in a,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.53,0:59:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,as you're progressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.49,0:59:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.09,0:59:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.09,0:59:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.89,0:59:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And the second question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.69,0:59:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.69,0:59:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,if you can explain to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.61,0:59:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you talked about someone with a presence
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.38,0:59:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that is up in the upper hundreds,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.88,0:59:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,counteracting the negativity of many,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.80,0:59:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.02,0:59:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens, globally,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.02,0:59:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,when you have a loss of many people from the Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.02,0:59:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,number one,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.02,0:59:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and number two,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.52,0:59:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,when someone who has a high level of being
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.02,0:59:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,leaves the planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.07,0:59:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about the collective consciousness level of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.07,0:59:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.32,0:59:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sustained, yes, considerably,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.00,1:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,by just a few, very advanced, yes,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because their energy field is so powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.00,1:00:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, when they leave the planet,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.28,1:00:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,will the collective energy field,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.28,1:00:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah, I don't think so, no,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.67,1:00:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the collective energy field will remain the same,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.67,1:00:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,because the vibration and the frequency of the aura
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.67,1:00:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is now in the collective.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.67,1:00:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.67,1:00:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.67,1:00:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The teachings of Jesus Christ go down centuries,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.67,1:00:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,even though he's not physically here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.67,1:00:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's like the aura, the energy field,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.18,1:00:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the vibration, the frequency,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.18,1:00:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,sustains that of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.76,1:00:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because otherwise,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.97,1:00:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise mankind,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.97,1:00:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in fact, we even asked one time,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.97,1:00:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,if it had not been for the great,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.97,1:00:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,great teachers,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.97,1:00:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,mankind would have extinguished itself by now,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.97,1:00:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and we always get yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.97,1:00:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.04,1:00:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He would have killed himself off, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.04,1:00:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.04,1:00:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.04,1:00:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I think of teachers such as yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.04,1:00:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,or Father Thomas Keating leaving the planet,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.04,1:00:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and I wonder,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.04,1:01:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,how will we be affected?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.04,1:01:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I think the aura,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.04,1:01:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field is still there.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.04,1:01:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.04,1:01:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.04,1:01:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call him.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.04,1:01:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.04,1:01:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give him a ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.04,1:01:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not go at the same time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.04,1:01:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I got to meet him,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.04,1:01:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.04,1:01:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and be with him up in Colorado.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.04,1:01:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Colorado.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.04,1:01:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where I'm from.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.07,1:01:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.07,1:01:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We got,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.07,1:01:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,we were at the,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.07,1:01:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,what's the name of it?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.07,1:01:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Benedict's?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.07,1:01:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Benedict's.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.07,1:01:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Benedict's.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.07,1:01:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.07,1:01:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.07,1:01:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.16,1:01:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is similar to the previous one.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.61,1:01:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that evolution of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.96,1:01:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,evolution of consciousness is accompanied by discharging pain
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.96,1:01:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as we go through levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.96,1:01:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And you said that the pain that one experiences at 800 and above
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.96,1:01:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is of the collective consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.18,1:01:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you differentiate those higher levels with lower levels?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.04,1:02:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say if you move to forgiveness,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.04,1:02:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,then you will also come up with the guilt
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.04,1:02:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of all the times you were not forgiving.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.04,1:02:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.40,1:02:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't that it's causing the pain,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.40,1:02:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but now through self-awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.40,1:02:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So part of spiritual work is overcoming the reluctance
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.40,1:02:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to look at the errors.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.40,1:02:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it can't be done without self-forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.40,1:02:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason we stress the innocence of the consciousness of mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.52,1:02:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is because the human mind,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.52,1:02:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the way it's put together,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.52,1:02:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot tell when it's making an error
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.52,1:02:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,without correction and information from outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.52,1:02:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So someone who has a higher level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.05,1:02:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,experiences the collective unconsciousness pain,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.05,1:02:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,or collective consciousness pain?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.05,1:02:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.05,1:02:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain is because it's inclusion in purity
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.15,1:02:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of something that's not pure,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.15,1:03:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and that impurity burns.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.30,1:03:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you look at it and see what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.30,1:03:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The biggest problem I had was with
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.00,1:03:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the Heart of the Spiritual Warrior.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.36,1:03:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Indignation.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.28,1:03:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I paid no attention to the world for a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.28,1:03:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I began to re-examine it,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.28,1:03:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,especially when I did Truth vs. Falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.28,1:03:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And indignation would come up out of my spiritual warrior.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.67,1:03:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had to constantly clear that,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.47,1:03:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to stop seeing people who create pain
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.47,1:03:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and suffering for others,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.47,1:03:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,stop being angry or indignant at them, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.47,1:03:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That didn't come up until that level,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.30,1:03:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,then it came up.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.30,1:03:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't personally indignant at it,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.87,1:03:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but collectively, I was.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.71,1:04:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of this lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.71,1:04:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been doubting my own intuition.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.71,1:04:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the early part of this year,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.93,1:04:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a period where that seemed to lift.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.93,1:04:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was doing calibrations, and they tied in,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.93,1:04:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and a lot of things happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.93,1:04:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And then that came in doubt.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.93,1:04:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And I notice you don't have doubt
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.93,1:04:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.93,1:04:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering when it calibrated that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.93,1:04:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.22,1:04:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's all kinds of doubt.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.22,1:04:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's different expressions,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.22,1:04:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,like cynicism, skepticism.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.22,1:04:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Skepticism is about 60.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.73,1:04:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Doubt can be a consequence of integrity,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.73,1:04:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,or it depends what the motivation is behind it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.83,1:04:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to be connected with despair,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.69,1:04:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in my case, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.69,1:04:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where it leads to.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.69,1:05:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So that would be the level, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.97,1:05:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Despair about what?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.00,1:05:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Life, or where I'm going,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.00,1:05:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,or my connection to God, or...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.31,1:05:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That would really take a little spiritual counseling
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.50,1:05:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to get to the basis of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.69,1:05:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The doubt, then, is a lack of faith.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.93,1:05:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're making faith conditional.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.93,1:05:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you make faith unconditional?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.66,1:05:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So you think if you pray,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.04,1:05:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,your leg's gonna get better.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.62,1:05:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.62,1:05:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It may not.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.62,1:05:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You see my thumb return?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.68,1:05:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.81,1:05:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Gone forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.81,1:05:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.81,1:05:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's what your expectation is of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.04,1:06:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Disillusionment means that you're putting something on God.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.06,1:06:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If I pray up a storm,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.06,1:06:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,God will let such and such thing happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.06,1:06:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about praying for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.41,1:06:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.41,1:06:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In terms of connecting with the inner self,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.41,1:06:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,or the intuition,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.44,1:06:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and trusting that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.44,1:06:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.44,1:06:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.44,1:06:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it's going external,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.44,1:06:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and checking if it...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.44,1:06:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It only takes something outside that
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.44,1:06:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to question it, and then...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.70,1:06:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.70,1:06:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It would require a session with you
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.70,1:06:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to really get to the basis of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.70,1:06:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finishing a book called
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.70,1:06:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Transcending Levels of Consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.70,1:06:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, this is finished.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.70,1:06:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In which we cover these subjects.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.70,1:06:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have the time today,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.70,1:06:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's a whole chapter on this very thing
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.70,1:06:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,with the various things that could be leading to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.70,1:06:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we had time,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.70,1:06:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,we would go through them.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.70,1:06:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Any one of them can be triggering it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.70,1:06:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And once you see it, you say,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.70,1:06:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.70,1:06:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,One I got earlier was the question,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.70,1:06:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,what's the juice in it?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.70,1:07:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the juice of doubt?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.70,1:07:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got that it's being the victim,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.70,1:07:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore getting people to be sorry
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.70,1:07:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,as a way of extracting...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.70,1:07:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, whether it could be
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.70,1:07:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,unconscious motivations, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.70,1:07:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.70,1:07:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're working on it, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.70,1:07:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're working on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.70,1:07:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.70,1:07:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.40,1:07:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're working on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.40,1:07:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.80,1:07:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't have time for questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.80,1:07:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, my question pertains
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.80,1:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to the calibration of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.80,1:07:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of groups of people.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.80,1:07:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You've indicated that excluding Karl Marx,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.80,1:07:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the great book's author's calibration goes up a bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.80,1:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take out Marx, yeah,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.00,1:07:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Marx at 130 brings down the whole level.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.00,1:07:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.00,1:07:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you take out Engels at 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.00,1:07:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.00,1:07:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole level,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.00,1:07:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the collective goes up, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.00,1:07:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.00,1:07:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.00,1:07:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The collective level of mankind right now
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.00,1:07:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is where it is,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.00,1:07:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because there's so many people at a very low level.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.00,1:08:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It brings down the overall average, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.00,1:08:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You've also calibrated the United States at 421,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.00,1:08:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and that half of the people in this country are under 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.00,1:08:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it useful to calibrate,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.00,1:08:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the folks in the United States are over 200
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.00,1:08:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and have another calibration?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.00,1:08:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't make sense of the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.15,1:08:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the same thing that you're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.15,1:08:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,with Karl Marx and the great book's authors.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.15,1:08:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.15,1:08:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking like a country out of that,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.15,1:08:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,would the world calibrate higher?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.15,1:08:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.15,1:08:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take the lowest countries off the planet, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.15,1:08:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What would the calibration of the folks in the United States be
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.15,1:08:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,excluding the 50% that are under 200?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.15,1:08:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.15,1:08:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was wondering about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.15,1:08:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too hypothetical for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.15,1:08:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.15,1:08:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.15,1:08:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it useful to do that sort of thing, or?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.15,1:08:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Could, I don't still get the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.15,1:08:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you do that sort of thing,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.15,1:08:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's a hypothetical question.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.15,1:09:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.15,1:09:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take out all the people that are below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.15,1:09:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.15,1:09:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what would the calibrated level of mankind,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.31,1:09:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of America be?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.31,1:09:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.31,1:09:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.31,1:09:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I did do it one time.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.31,1:09:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.31,1:09:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.31,1:09:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We can answer that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.43,1:09:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We did do it one time.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.43,1:09:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be over 475, 480.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.59,1:09:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be around 475 instead of 421.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.59,1:09:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, is it useful to use the mode and the median also besides the mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.59,1:09:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this is the mean, but it's a logarithmic scale.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.59,1:09:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.59,1:09:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're confusing mathematics and statistics with consciousness level.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.59,1:09:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a different thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.59,1:09:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not comparable.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.59,1:09:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.16,1:09:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.16,1:09:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.16,1:09:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.16,1:09:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.16,1:09:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.16,1:09:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.16,1:09:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.16,1:09:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.16,1:09:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.16,1:09:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.16,1:09:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.16,1:09:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.16,1:09:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.16,1:09:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.16,1:09:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.16,1:09:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.16,1:09:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.16,1:09:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.16,1:09:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.66,1:09:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.66,1:09:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.66,1:09:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.66,1:09:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.66,1:09:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.66,1:09:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.30,1:09:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one question each because we only have about 15 more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.30,1:09:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get over it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.30,1:10:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be very quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.30,1:10:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no question.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.30,1:10:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Only thank you very much for blessing from last year.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.30,1:10:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is the book for children about unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.30,1:10:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I had experience with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.92,1:10:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When I said I give the Holy Spirit in a moment, I feel huge powerful field of energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.30,1:10:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,powerful, but peaceful. So my book was there up, so I don't know what happened with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.30,1:10:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good. Thank you very much. And I have eight books for anybody who likes, loves cats.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.30,1:10:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Like cats, right here. Like cats.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.30,1:10:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a kitty book.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.30,1:10:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't know if I could give to anybody. And thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.30,1:10:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the kitty book. My kitty thanks you, I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.11,1:10:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It keeps us human, pets, doesn't it? Keeps us considerate of others.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.81,1:11:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,People who live alone and get depressed, I say to them, do you have a dog?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.81,1:11:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I say, well I'm not going to treat you unless you get a dog or a cat.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.80,1:11:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to treat you unless you get a dog or a cat.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.09,1:11:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They would get better right away, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.22,1:11:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one question.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.22,1:11:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.22,1:11:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who and why create other dimension, astral and entities?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.70,1:11:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who creates what?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.70,1:11:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who and why create other dimension, astral and entities?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.70,1:11:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about other dimensions. I got enough trouble with this.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.70,1:11:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who created other dimensions?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.70,1:11:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell you. That's not my province.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.85,1:11:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have enough trouble with this dimension. You?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.92,1:11:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just curious about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.92,1:12:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I teach avoid other dimensions, see. Avoid investigating the paranormal.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.92,1:12:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know, but it's just who created.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.92,1:12:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't think it's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.92,1:12:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,People, you've got to be an expert, an expert, expert, expert.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.92,1:12:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Very few people are super expert, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.20,1:12:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.20,1:12:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't even know they're out of body. They tell you about astral realms.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.20,1:12:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They think they went there, their astral body went there.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.20,1:12:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And people who visit those places and come back with all their earth prophecies are dead wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.51,1:12:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,California did not fall off in the ocean and all the rest of the crap that went on in the 80s.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.54,1:12:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just slide up because we need you closer to the mic.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.54,1:12:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We should have guys at Sedona there, give you a date when Sedona,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.54,1:12:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,California's going to fall off in the ocean, Phoenix is going to be a harbor, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.54,1:12:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's going to be ravaging gangs, pillaging, and there's going to be this and that.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.54,1:12:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.62,1:13:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time for this event came and went and it didn't happen,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.62,1:13:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,he would just change the dates and go on giving lectures.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.74,1:13:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.84,1:13:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Asking about an avatar in India by the name of Sri Kalki Bhagavan and his wife Amma.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.38,1:13:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the age of four, he told his parents he was going to enlighten the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.80,1:13:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's now in his 70s or 80s and is having his followers perform what he calls a diksha or diksha.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.80,1:13:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.80,1:13:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where they...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.80,1:13:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.80,1:13:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands on where they open the...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.80,1:13:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.80,1:13:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For $5,500, you can go there.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.80,1:13:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.80,1:13:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.05,1:13:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.05,1:13:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,For $5,500, you can get diksha.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.05,1:13:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He says that...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.05,1:13:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to give you a diksha for a dollar and a half.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.05,1:13:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a buck?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.05,1:13:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.05,1:13:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.05,1:13:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you, my beloved, in your perfection.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.05,1:13:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So he says that...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.05,1:13:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides all the wisdom of eternity.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.05,1:13:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to go for diksha.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.05,1:13:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You just got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.05,1:13:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.05,1:13:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.05,1:13:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.07,1:13:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.76,1:13:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.76,1:13:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.76,1:13:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.76,1:14:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.60,1:14:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.60,1:14:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.60,1:14:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.20,1:14:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.20,1:14:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.20,1:14:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.33,1:14:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She just got diksha.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.33,1:14:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.33,1:14:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell by her eyes she got diksha.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.12,1:14:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell by her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.12,1:14:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.12,1:14:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.12,1:14:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.16,1:14:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's the...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.16,1:14:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.16,1:14:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.16,1:14:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,On one of your videos, you mentioned to work on the resolve, but it's your final moments
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.16,1:14:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to work on the resolve
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.40,1:14:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to die for God
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.08,1:14:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to get that now
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.58,1:14:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're presented with that
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.96,1:14:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I have
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.99,1:14:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.35,1:14:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but fears
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.79,1:14:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,arise on their own
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.19,1:14:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,fear of death
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.95,1:14:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,fear of non-existence
