Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.01,1:15:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I know fear is an illusion
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.23,1:15:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but do I meet that fear
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.67,1:15:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,or do I just
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.03,1:15:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,oh it's very innate
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.35,1:15:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,very deep
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.01,1:15:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the basis of all fears
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.75,1:15:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I teach a mythic call
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.99,1:15:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and then what
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.57,1:15:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so you say you can lose all your money
