Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.64,1:15:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I'll be lonely
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.44,1:15:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and then what
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.04,1:15:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and I won't be able to get a job
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.08,1:15:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and then what
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.62,1:15:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I won't have any money
