Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.24,1:15:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'll have to live in a park
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.66,1:15:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and be friendless
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.80,1:15:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and then what
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.42,1:15:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I'll get sick
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.74,1:15:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and then what
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.88,1:15:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and then nobody will care for me
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.04,1:15:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I'll get a disease
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.08,1:15:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I'll starve to death
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.58,1:15:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and every single fear you'll find
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.16,1:15:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,will come down to a fear of death
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.64,1:15:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that underlies every fear
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.44,1:15:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but how do you work to transcend that fear of death
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.16,1:15:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you keep surrendering to the
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.74,1:15:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and then what
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.50,1:15:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you it's great to be a bag man
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.56,1:15:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you how you live
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.55,1:15:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you live in the park
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.63,1:15:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,it's fantastic
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.43,1:15:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you go to the bank
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.81,1:16:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you read the wall street journal
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.15,1:16:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,they have free cookies and free coffee
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.57,1:16:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it's cool being a bag man
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.20,1:16:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.66,1:16:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not worried about form life
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.64,1:16:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the cross over
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.60,1:16:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the death that I
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.30,1:16:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean I guess my question is
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.66,1:16:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,meeting the fear of death
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.60,1:16:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,not the things leading to that
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.84,1:16:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,alright so it's only a fear like any other fear
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.64,1:16:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,alright
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.48,1:16:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the way to surrender fear
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.84,1:16:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just finish the chapter on it
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.00,1:16:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is stop calling it anything
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.28,1:16:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,don't call it fear
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.34,1:16:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not experiencing fear
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.50,1:16:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a label
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.64,1:16:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a nominalization word
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.50,1:16:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,F-E-A-R
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.84,1:16:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't experience fear
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.64,1:16:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't experience F-E-A-R
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.64,1:16:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.14,1:16:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you experience a particular set of symptoms
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.14,1:16:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,let go of resisting the symptoms
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.64,1:16:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,if you completely let go of resisting the symptoms
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.64,1:16:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the symptoms will go away
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.64,1:16:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and so will what you call fear
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.64,1:17:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that's how you can disappear anything
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.28,1:17:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're presented with what you think is
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.30,1:17:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not going to face dying
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.26,1:17:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's surely
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.26,1:17:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you come up to me and say
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.56,1:17:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,if you come up against what you feel
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.56,1:17:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is the necessity to surrender your life to God
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.56,1:17:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,then you do so
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.56,1:17:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,because you can't die
