Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.86,1:17:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not a possibility
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.86,1:17:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's an experiential reality
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.96,1:17:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it's only when you face it
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.69,1:17:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and when you actually die
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.69,1:17:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you feel yourself die
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.69,1:17:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you literally do die
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.20,1:17:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,there's an agony of death
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.20,1:17:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and then eternal life
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.20,1:17:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,keep that in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.40,1:17:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is on the other side of the door
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.40,1:17:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can't cheat your way through it
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.52,1:17:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were going to tell her
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.77,1:17:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,okay that's right
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.77,1:18:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,no you're right on it
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.77,1:18:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,underlying every fear is fear of death
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.00,1:18:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and once you lose your fear of death
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.00,1:18:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.00,1:18:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing can really get to you anymore
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.08,1:18:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why people who have had near death experiences
