Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.92,1:18:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,facilitates his acceptance of it
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.92,1:18:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and both of us
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.92,1:18:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,through the without fear
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.92,1:18:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
