Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.92,1:18:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.92,1:18:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,mm-hmm
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.64,1:18:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean worst thing to happen is you die
