Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.64,1:18:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.63,1:18:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.63,1:18:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan how are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.63,1:18:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dwal Kul in one of the Alice Bailey books
