Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.24,1:19:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is a unique condition your incarnation different than what the buddha stated happened to him and
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.84,1:19:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,different from krishna because jesus was both man and god simultaneously right yeah so within the
