Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.61,1:20:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,in and of yourself without the help of a savior the likelihood of you getting to heaven is slim
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.88,1:20:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the truth therefore on judgment day the christ will speak for you and be your advocate
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.59,1:20:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah it's an honor yes um i have here a publication um published in 1968 um that i have
