Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.23,1:21:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,um the title of it is the vitamin b3 therapy a second communication to a a physicians
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.59,1:21:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,from bill w who we now know as bill wilson the founder of paul it's anonymous
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.62,1:21:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,um it goes on to say that um alcoholics suffering from depression anxiety tension
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.74,1:21:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and exhaustion can can be helped with these these techniques yeah sugar-free diet you're going to be
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.98,1:21:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,a fascination
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.10,1:21:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so the question is um would you still still support this this publication because you
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.72,1:21:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a couple articles in here authored by you and and um do you have any further comments
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.93,1:21:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,for for about about b3 therapy no this was uh our clinical experience at this time
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.16,1:21:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so we got hopeless hopeless uh psychotic alcoholics etc from all over the place the first thing we'd do
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.56,1:21:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,time so we got hopeless hopeless uh psychotic alcoholics etc from all over the place
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.32,1:21:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing we did is took them off, you got to stop all sugar and sweets, take big
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.74,1:22:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,doses of vitamin B3, and if you need the pharmacologic agent to stop being crazy, then you do that
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.94,1:22:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,too.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.94,1:22:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And we had a tremendous recovery with hopeless cases, see.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.82,1:22:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And Bill Wilson was the first one, because Bill suffered intractable depression.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.40,1:22:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the founder of AA, who himself had a high, very high experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.83,1:22:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of those worms lighting up like that radiated out into the recovery of millions
