Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.19,1:22:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just not thinking at the moment, because of the time pressure.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.19,1:23:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, so niacin, sugar-free diet, niacin recoveries, we covered the depression.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.19,1:23:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.19,1:23:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And Bill told people about it, and we tried it on lots of people, and by God, it worked.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.99,1:23:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.61,1:23:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.61,1:23:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.57,1:23:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in the mid-'80s, I had a tattoo put on my back, a full mural I put on my back.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.11,1:23:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.11,1:23:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was kind of my conception of creation and destruction and life and death at the
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.33,1:23:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,time.
