Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.33,1:23:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of the yin and yang, the alpha omega.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.33,1:23:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The dance of Shiva.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.36,1:23:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.36,1:23:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.36,1:23:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.36,1:23:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And since, everything has changed for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.36,1:23:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.36,1:23:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.36,1:23:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, this represented complete opposites, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.36,1:23:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.36,1:23:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Creation, destruction, life, death, the road of life, and so forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.36,1:23:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.36,1:23:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was just wondering.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.36,1:23:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's some negative images.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.59,1:23:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.59,1:23:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's some negative images in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.59,1:23:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I know there is some negative images amongst this.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.59,1:23:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.59,1:23:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We need a good artist to create them differently.
