Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.59,1:24:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really bother me mentally.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.34,1:24:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.34,1:24:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know that the images are negative now.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.34,1:24:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.34,1:24:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know that negative images have an energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.34,1:24:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
