Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.44,1:33:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I see the difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.44,1:33:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.44,1:33:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a very simple way I just discovered recently.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.44,1:33:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you have any books around here.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.18,1:33:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.18,1:33:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold Bin Laden in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.68,1:33:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I just use him as a bad example currently because Hitler's dead, you know, but I...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.98,1:33:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitler used to be a real man.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.86,1:33:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't very reliable, but he left us, so a bad example, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.62,1:33:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.62,1:33:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've got a big, heavy dictionary at home.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.00,1:33:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I hold in mind a statement.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.40,1:33:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I lift the book.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.08,1:33:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I hold in mind the alternate to that statement and I lift the book.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.22,1:33:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,With very little experience you'll get, when I hold Jesus Christ in mind, the book comes
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.26,1:33:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,up pretty easily.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.26,1:34:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When I hold Bin Laden in mind, it takes up more muscle power.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.70,1:34:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So the simplest, fastest way I've discovered most recently is just lifting.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.86,1:34:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, things that are heavy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.24,1:34:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And you notice that when you're thinking something positive, you're much stronger.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.08,1:34:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I always tell people, you know, if you're in sports, at the starting gun, hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.62,1:34:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the victory of your country, God, womanhood, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.88,1:34:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Something beyond your personal self to win because if I want to win, that's already kinesiologically
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.06,1:34:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,knocked me out and I just lost a tenth of a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.62,1:34:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.62,1:34:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.62,1:34:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do it for my university, for the good of mankind, if I do it for womanhood, then
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.66,1:34:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already got more power.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.20,1:34:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell a woman athlete, do it for, you know, womanhood.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.68,1:34:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That instantly gives her more power.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.96,1:34:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If a dude does it so I get to win the tennis championship, she's already weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.28,1:35:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So at the starting gun, the one who does it for a higher purpose has more power, measurable
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.73,1:35:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,power.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.73,1:35:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.08,1:35:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.08,1:35:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When you run, run for God, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.98,1:35:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.98,1:35:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.98,1:35:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, my question has to do with, I've been kind of having like some spiritual experiences
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.11,1:35:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,where I become aware of like my heart chakra.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.28,1:35:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I don't know what to call it, but that's kind of how I word it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.34,1:35:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And when it happens, I feel like my heart is like overjoyed with love.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.72,1:35:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And then like sometimes an hour, sometimes a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.63,1:35:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I still feel that same heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.27,1:35:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's almost like it's black or dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.27,1:35:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, like, but then it comes back again and it fluctuates like constantly throughout
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.27,1:35:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the day sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.36,1:35:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes it's more constant.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.36,1:35:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just kind of curious if you have anything to say about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.36,1:35:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if that's really a question, but.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.77,1:35:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How to handle this kundalini energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.77,1:35:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.00,1:35:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.00,1:35:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can breathe it up to our chakras.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.00,1:35:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea that it's gone, it's not gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.00,1:35:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.00,1:35:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.00,1:35:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.00,1:35:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.00,1:35:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.89,1:36:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.89,1:36:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.89,1:36:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.08,1:36:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.08,1:36:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.24,1:36:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.24,1:36:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.24,1:36:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.76,1:36:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.76,1:36:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.76,1:36:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.76,1:36:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.94,1:36:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.97,1:36:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.97,1:36:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.97,1:36:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.97,1:36:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.97,1:36:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.97,1:36:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It really, you really require sort of a teacher of the, of that kind of a technique.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.36,1:36:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I would breathe it up to the higher chakras all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.36,1:36:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.36,1:36:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the heart is, is, is very, very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.12,1:36:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can go breathe it to the crown chakra.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.12,1:36:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.12,1:36:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I feel it there.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.12,1:36:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it to the throat.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.12,1:36:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, do it to the third eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.12,1:36:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Try that.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.12,1:36:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just breathe it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.12,1:36:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.12,1:36:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.12,1:36:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.12,1:36:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you a question about my five pregnancies.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.32,1:36:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,About?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.30,1:36:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,About?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.30,1:36:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,About?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.30,1:37:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,About?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.30,1:37:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,About what? Pregnancies. I had three pregnancies during the 20-year use of drugs and alcohol that ended in abortion.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.40,1:37:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The last, after February the 8th of 89, I cleaned up and two years later had a son in two years.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.81,1:37:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering what you can tell me about that karma or maybe the purposes of the two sons that lived.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.80,1:37:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand the question. Some lived, some died?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.83,1:37:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Two. I have two now that are alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.92,1:37:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Two boys are alive and yet she did have some...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.92,1:37:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stillbirths or something?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.92,1:37:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Abortions.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.92,1:37:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Abortions.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.92,1:37:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is your question about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.92,1:37:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.92,1:37:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Abortions before three months, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.92,1:38:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the amount of guilt you feel about it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.24,1:38:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Our research is that the spirit doesn't enter the embryo until the third month.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.62,1:38:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only, you know, it's the physicality which becomes human.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.62,1:38:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But the spirit won't enter the fetus until the third month.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.19,1:38:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we got, you know, we did test that out.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.19,1:38:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We were testing out contraception,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.19,1:38:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,first trisemester, so a late abortion has a different karma consequence, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.81,1:38:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive yourself anyway, no matter what you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.81,1:38:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I think all women deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.61,1:38:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they have a good karma just for birthing the human race, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.96,1:38:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. I have a question about kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.96,1:38:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When you are doing a calibration,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.96,1:38:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and someone is in the room that has an attachment
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.96,1:39:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to what the result might be, does it, can it skew the results?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.96,1:39:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not their being in the room, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.96,1:39:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. If they're part of the test, either the arm or...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.96,1:39:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're part of the test, sure, that's going to throw it off, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.96,1:39:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.96,1:39:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you just, you can't have a stake in the results.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.96,1:39:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.96,1:39:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I tell people, forget any stake in the result.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.96,1:39:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try to find the absolute truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.96,1:39:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, and then if the answer isn't what you want,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.96,1:39:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you can begin to ask more questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.96,1:39:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And by the time you finish those questions,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.96,1:39:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,then the way you contextualize it will have changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.96,1:39:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And it'll be okay that you got what you got.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.96,1:39:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.44,1:39:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you missed the plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.44,1:39:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,With kinesiology, you find that that plane was scheduled to crash.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.44,1:39:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.72,1:39:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your teaching. I love you both.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.72,1:39:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You said something earlier that I missed.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.72,1:39:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your voice dropped at the end of a sentence,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.72,1:40:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just wanted to ask you what it was that you said.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.72,1:40:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that it's only coming out now,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.72,1:40:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but that nine people at the highest levels of government that are...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.72,1:40:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't get the rest of what you said.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.72,1:40:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There are moles.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.72,1:40:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.72,1:40:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we picked out moles in the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.72,1:40:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, in fact, it's on the record.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.72,1:40:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think we did on power versus forest, one of the first ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.30,1:40:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We picked out two very famous ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.30,1:40:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.46,1:40:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,One was...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.81,1:40:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell were they?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.81,1:40:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard Aldrich.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.04,1:40:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, one was Aldrich.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.04,1:40:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other was Aldrich...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.26,1:40:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,One was Aldrich James, and the other one was Hanson.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.26,1:40:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanson.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.26,1:40:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Well, I just...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.64,1:40:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We picked them out years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.64,1:40:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we said when we wrote the book,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.64,1:40:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,currently, how many is there?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.74,1:40:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.74,1:40:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.74,1:40:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I think one came out this last week, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.74,1:40:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in the White House.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.74,1:40:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.74,1:40:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.74,1:41:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.94,1:41:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, where else would you find them?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.94,1:41:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was a spy, I wouldn't be out in the garage.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.73,1:41:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be in the White House with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.47,1:41:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be at Los Alamos with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.50,1:41:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where they were, Los Alamos.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.60,1:41:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.60,1:41:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think they're going to be?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.60,1:41:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You talked about what you hold in mind is what you experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.60,1:41:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought after finishing the Course in Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.60,1:41:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to take a specific phrase from your teaching.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.60,1:41:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, nothing is causing anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.60,1:41:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.60,1:41:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.60,1:41:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is happening spontaneously of its own,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.60,1:41:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and as expression of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.76,1:41:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And the question is, should I do it like the Course in Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.76,1:41:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that I replace every thought with the phrase,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.76,1:41:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,or just hold it in mind silently,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.76,1:41:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because then it's nondualistic, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.76,1:42:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When doing the Course in Miracles, does he...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.95,1:42:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, actually, it has nothing to do with the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.95,1:42:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't quite get the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.95,1:42:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he mean doing the lessons?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.95,1:42:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.95,1:42:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Pulling the lessons as a fact?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.95,1:42:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.43,1:42:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of a probability.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.43,1:42:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're a little confused on the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.43,1:42:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to take the phrase from him,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.43,1:42:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that nothing is causing anything,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.43,1:42:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and take this phrase and hold this phrase in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.43,1:42:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you can meditate on a phrase, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.43,1:42:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.43,1:42:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And the question is, should I do it like the Course in Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.43,1:42:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that replace every thought and everything with the phrase?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.43,1:42:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You could, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.43,1:42:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Or like more...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.43,1:42:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it silently, because then it's nondualistic.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.43,1:42:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.78,1:42:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.78,1:42:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.78,1:42:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.78,1:42:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.78,1:42:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.29,1:42:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.29,1:42:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have the commitment now to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.29,1:42:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.29,1:42:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a vis-a-vis to the Guru, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.29,1:42:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So my ego can...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.29,1:42:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.29,1:42:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.29,1:43:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So my ego cannot escape now.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.68,1:43:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold in mind, you hold in mind the optimal, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.68,1:43:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it's up to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.77,1:43:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.71,1:43:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.00,1:43:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I first have a confession.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.73,1:43:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized recently that my devotion has been to getting spiritual experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.05,1:43:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And because I see all the description of the defined state,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.21,1:43:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,like the allness, the void, the beauty, the unconditional love,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.21,1:43:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was attracted to all those.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.21,1:43:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was doing all kind of practice, meditation, breathing,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.21,1:43:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,contemplation in order to get those.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.21,1:43:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And I realized it wasn't the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.21,1:44:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The devotion should be to nonduality instead.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.21,1:44:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And those experience follows.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.50,1:44:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.50,1:44:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, true.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.50,1:44:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I'd like to share that first of all.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.49,1:44:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.49,1:44:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a wonderful insight.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.56,1:44:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the reason I call it devotional nonduality is because there's the way of negation, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.97,1:44:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But the way of devotion is coming from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.97,1:44:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of negating love, it's love that motivates the desire to become enlightened, let's say.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.97,1:44:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So you use the power of the heart rather than just spiritual ambition.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.97,1:44:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.97,1:44:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question for people below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.97,1:44:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they accountable for what they do?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.10,1:44:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.10,1:44:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So what they do and choose have consequence.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.10,1:44:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But they reject that responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.20,1:44:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but they're still responsible.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.39,1:45:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, they didn't mean to skid on the ice, but frankly, your car is overturning,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.25,1:45:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,blocking traffic.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.25,1:45:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So it may be an innocent intention, but nevertheless, you're still responsible to call a tow truck,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.18,1:45:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,get your car pulled away, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.18,1:45:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.18,1:45:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.18,1:45:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And what advice would you give to those below 200 if they want to be above 200?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.69,1:45:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.69,1:45:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Make the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.74,1:45:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray, yeah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.74,1:45:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the collective spiritual energy, the collective spiritual energy of groups is very
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.41,1:45:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,influential.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.41,1:45:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200, I tell people, join the nearest 12-step group, the First of Miracles group,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.73,1:45:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,go to church.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.73,1:45:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Put yourself in the energy field, you know, and then sometime when you're not even trying
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.99,1:45:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it, all of a sudden, you sort of get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.99,1:45:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.99,1:45:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.99,1:45:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called getting it by osmosis.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.99,1:45:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.99,1:46:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So I tell people, immerse yourself in a spiritual group of high integrity and follow their teachings
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.99,1:46:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to the best of your possibility, and the rest will be up to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.18,1:46:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.18,1:46:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You get it by osmosis.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.18,1:46:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.44,1:46:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just cutting out.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.44,1:46:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.50,1:46:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.50,1:46:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.50,1:46:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one more internal...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.50,1:46:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It went out to the microphone.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.50,1:46:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No mics?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.50,1:46:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.50,1:46:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.50,1:46:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.53,1:46:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.53,1:46:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.53,1:46:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.75,1:46:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.82,1:46:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All my copious notes, I have not been able to formulate an actual question.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.59,1:46:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.59,1:46:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.68,1:46:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The area of interest or elucidation is the spiritual will, my spiritual will.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.68,1:47:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.04,1:47:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmic propensity and the paradigm shifts you speak of.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.38,1:47:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.38,1:47:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Specifically, in my case right now, the burning sensation with the purification process.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.92,1:47:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.92,1:47:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these things attract, get my attention.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.92,1:47:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.92,1:47:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, I haven't been able to correlate a thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.30,1:47:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.30,1:47:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To ask a direct question.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.30,1:47:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.30,1:47:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a direct question?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.97,1:47:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the brain physiology as consciousness advance, and the praying for...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.16,1:47:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My brain burns.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.16,1:47:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had brain burns.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.09,1:47:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.44,1:47:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had brain burns for the past two years.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.44,1:47:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been in almost constant meditation and prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.04,1:48:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm thinking I hear in this lecture is resolution of karmic propensity through intense
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.71,1:48:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,prayer and meditation.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.71,1:48:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.71,1:48:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're moving too fast, you're gonna stress yourself, so you're complaining about the
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.71,1:48:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,stress.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.71,1:48:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.71,1:48:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I like that answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.71,1:48:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.80,1:48:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.80,1:48:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.80,1:48:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's attraction.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.80,1:48:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yin instead of yang.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.80,1:48:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going at it too yang.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.80,1:48:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yin is, I invite thee, oh Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.96,1:48:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yang is, say you're too yang.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.96,1:48:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.96,1:48:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Try being more yin.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.04,1:48:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.04,1:48:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life becomes a prayer, a devotional mudra.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.76,1:48:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,By my positionality, do I invite thee, oh Lord, who reigns over all.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.76,1:48:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.14,1:48:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's more like supplication, invitation, the power of the yin.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.14,1:48:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going at it like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.14,1:48:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.33,1:48:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.33,1:48:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.33,1:48:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
