Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.60,1:49:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, every question that's answered brings up a new question,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.38,1:49:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,which, of course, is again my delight.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.20,1:49:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want to tell you how much I enjoyed being with you today.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.33,1:49:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It was sort of a different experience, experiential this morning, experiential this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.99,1:50:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I do give thanks to thee, O Lord, for this, thy gift to me, those assembled.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.17,1:50:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You are God's gift to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.81,1:50:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.04,1:50:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the bag, Clive.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.13,1:50:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.93,1:50:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I had trouble talking after that, you know, because it brings up tears and everybody a lump in their throat.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.35,1:50:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a hard time continuing to talk after that.
